data.description: This beautiful property located at 412 SE Lancelot Ln is a stunning two-story family home, offering ample space for comfortable living. The home has received brand new carpet and LVP flooring, a whole house paint job including the exterior and a brand new garage door. With 4 bedrooms and 2 1/2 bathrooms, this home is perfect for a growing family or those in need of extra room for guests. The kitchen in this home is truly unique, featuring a round design that adds a touch of elegance to the overall aesthetic. Some of the essential appliances in the kitchen include a refrigerator, dishwasher and a brand new stove. The living room and dining room areas provide a great place for indoor entertaining, and the partial carpeting throughout these spaces adds warmth and comfort. Additionally, this home features wood and ceramic tile flooring that is both beautiful and durable. The laundry room, with its ample storage area, makes doing laundry simple and convenient. The vaulted ceilings contribute to the overall grandeur of the home, while the fireplace provides a cozy place to relax and unwind during colder months. Call listing agent - Carrie Austin at (580)512-6647 to schedule a tour today!  Brand NEW roof has been installed & skylights in living room are being removed due to recent hail storm.
